{"action":"created","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/8472","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/8472/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/8472/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/8472/events","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/issues/8472","id":43921745,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0MzkyMTc0NQ==","number":8472,"title":"RFC: staged / meta / generated types ?","user":{"login":"Jutho","id":4162102,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxNjIxMDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4162102?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho","html_url":"https://github.com/Jutho","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jutho/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":97639,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw5NzYzOQ==","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/speculative","name":"speculative","color":"999999","default":false,"description":"Whether the change will be implemented is speculative"},{"id":210700,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyMTA3MDA=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/decision","name":"decision","color":"F08000","default":false,"description":"A decision on this change is needed"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":14,"created_at":"2014-09-25T13:55:42Z","updated_at":"2024-01-04T11:08:13Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"Now that we have staged functions (or whatever name that will converge out of the discussion in #7474), can we be more greedy and request something similar to define types, i.e. where the type definition depends on the value of the parameters in a more general way than can currently be expressed?

